WEBVTT

02:09.270 --> 02:14.610
[REBIRTH]

02:15.070 --> 02:17.590
[Episode 22]

02:18.400 --> 02:19.590
Urgent dispatch!

02:20.710 --> 02:22.150
Great victory at Longyin Pass!

02:22.150 --> 02:23.800
Great victory at Longyin Pass!

02:23.800 --> 02:24.520
Qiao won.

02:24.680 --> 02:25.470
Qiao won!

02:25.520 --> 02:26.360
Qiao won!

02:26.840 --> 02:27.400
Look!

02:27.420 --> 02:28.520
This is the victory report!

02:28.520 --> 02:29.960
Which one of you
pushed for peace back then?

02:29.960 --> 02:31.360
Aren't you ashamed of yourselves?

02:31.360 --> 02:32.120
Was it you?

02:33.470 --> 02:34.240
Was it you?

02:34.470 --> 02:35.270
Your Majesty,

02:35.400 --> 02:36.400
it wasn't me.

02:39.079 --> 02:41.280
Qiao has achieved extraordinary merit.

02:41.280 --> 02:43.910
I'll appoint her
as the Left General of Cavalry!

02:43.910 --> 02:44.710
Your Majesty,

02:44.840 --> 02:46.960
that is my post.

02:47.400 --> 02:48.820
Then, Right General of Cavalry!

02:48.820 --> 02:50.590
That is General Li Qi's post.

02:50.800 --> 02:51.600
Right, right.

02:51.670 --> 02:53.670
I must think of an even grander title

02:53.800 --> 02:54.840
for her.

03:11.850 --> 03:13.710
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

03:18.750 --> 03:20.150
Please rise, both of you.

03:24.870 --> 03:26.470
Chu Qiao has defeated Yan Xun

03:26.470 --> 03:28.329
and will soon return to Tangjing.

03:28.560 --> 03:30.000
We must act immediately.

03:30.280 --> 03:32.590
Otherwise, once Li Ce
consolidates his grip on the throne,

03:32.590 --> 03:34.520
it will be hard for us to make a move.

03:34.560 --> 03:36.310
Are your troops ready?

03:36.630 --> 03:38.910
They will reach
the outskirts of Tangjing tonight.

03:38.910 --> 03:40.470
With a single order from you,

03:40.470 --> 03:42.120
we will march straight

03:42.120 --> 03:43.400
into the capital!

03:43.710 --> 03:45.120
In recent days, we've been spreading word

03:45.120 --> 03:46.840
of the Xuri Palace incident.

03:47.079 --> 03:48.750
All of Tangjing is buzzing with rumor.

03:48.750 --> 03:50.680
The truth
behind Crown Prince Maocheng's death

03:50.680 --> 03:52.150
has come to light,

03:52.280 --> 03:53.710
and the whereabouts of his heir

03:53.710 --> 03:55.360
have thrown the city into an uproar.

03:55.360 --> 03:56.220
Your Highness,

03:56.400 --> 03:58.600
it's time to reveal your true identity.

03:59.750 --> 04:00.610
Your Highness,

04:00.750 --> 04:02.520
I served Crown Prince Maocheng

04:02.520 --> 04:03.630
and have been lying in wait until now.

04:03.630 --> 04:05.840
For so many years, we've endured
humiliation and hardship,

04:05.840 --> 04:07.310
waiting for the right moment.

04:07.310 --> 04:08.900
Now that moment has come.

04:09.120 --> 04:10.630
We must strike immediately!

04:10.630 --> 04:12.400
We must take advantage of the chaos

04:12.400 --> 04:15.330
to reclaim
what is rightfully yours, Your Highness.

04:21.750 --> 04:27.430
[Tangjing]

04:56.190 --> 04:57.070
Your Majesty is here again,

04:57.070 --> 04:58.600
waiting for General Xiuli?

04:59.920 --> 05:01.120
This is the highest spot

05:01.120 --> 05:03.780
in Tangjing, where you can see
all the way north.

05:03.800 --> 05:04.870
If Qiao comes back,

05:05.160 --> 05:06.070
I'll be

05:06.360 --> 05:08.090
the first to spot her from here.

05:08.600 --> 05:09.060
Come on.

05:20.560 --> 05:21.220
Be careful!

05:27.070 --> 05:27.680
Thank you.

05:34.240 --> 05:36.240
Ever since General Xiuli came here,

05:36.750 --> 05:38.610
Your Majesty has been fond of her.

05:39.270 --> 05:40.830
Now that she's away on campaign,

05:40.830 --> 05:43.159
Your Majesty worries about her every day.

05:43.250 --> 05:44.620
If General Xiuli knew,

05:45.000 --> 05:46.720
she would surely be moved
by Your Majesty's devotion.

05:46.720 --> 05:47.310
Her?

05:48.680 --> 05:49.750
No way she would.

05:50.080 --> 05:52.140
She only likes fighting and warfare.

05:52.240 --> 05:52.920
And I don't want to

05:52.920 --> 05:54.630
tie her down with my feelings.

05:55.720 --> 05:56.390
But

05:57.310 --> 05:58.510
when Qiao comes back,

05:58.920 --> 06:00.120
I'll definitely give her

06:00.120 --> 06:01.070
a grand title—

06:01.510 --> 06:04.290
something even greater
than Sun Di's and Li Qi's combined.

06:04.290 --> 06:05.380
To thank her for

06:06.120 --> 06:08.650
protecting the territory of Biantang
for me.

06:11.070 --> 06:11.680
Li Yan,

06:12.480 --> 06:13.310
you read a lot.

06:14.830 --> 06:15.720
Help me see

06:16.040 --> 06:18.300
if the title I've come up with
is any good.

06:22.760 --> 06:23.510
Okay.

06:37.310 --> 06:38.360
Why?

06:38.680 --> 06:40.280
I never intended to kill you,

06:41.270 --> 06:44.000
but we were destined to end up like this.

06:47.040 --> 06:48.000
What a pity.

06:49.430 --> 06:50.360
You will never get to see

06:50.360 --> 06:52.680
your beloved General Chu return.

07:11.630 --> 07:12.600
Qiao...

07:14.680 --> 07:15.680
I can no longer

07:16.720 --> 07:17.830
protect you...

08:43.840 --> 08:44.700
Your Highness,

08:44.750 --> 08:47.000
5,000 imperial guards from nine city gates

08:47.000 --> 08:47.890
of Tangjing

08:47.920 --> 08:49.510
have assembled at the North Gate.

08:49.510 --> 08:51.510
A total of 200 gate sentries
have been stationed

08:51.510 --> 08:53.080
at all six gates
on the east and west sides,

08:53.080 --> 08:54.440
awaiting Your Highness's orders.

08:54.440 --> 08:54.960
Additionally,

08:54.960 --> 08:57.440
garrison troops from Lingnan and Lingdong

08:57.440 --> 08:59.390
have been deployed 30 li outside Tangjing.

08:59.390 --> 09:00.360
Should anything arise,

09:00.360 --> 09:03.420
they can enter the capital immediately
to protect you!

09:08.390 --> 09:09.000
-Your subjects,
-Your subjects,

09:09.000 --> 09:10.000
-Xu Su,
-Pei Jian,

09:10.000 --> 09:11.270
respectfully welcome Your Majesty!

09:11.270 --> 09:13.390
Long live Your Majesty!

09:13.670 --> 09:15.210
We respectfully welcome Your Majesty!

09:15.210 --> 09:16.920
Long live Your Majesty!

10:11.450 --> 10:12.360
Qiao...

10:14.390 --> 10:16.270
I can't wait for you anymore.

10:27.750 --> 10:28.630
I'm way better

10:28.630 --> 10:30.070
than that stone-faced Zhuge Yue.

10:30.070 --> 10:33.690
♪ The dust in the world ♪

10:30.320 --> 10:32.470
I'm handsome, suave,

10:32.470 --> 10:33.800
elegant, and graceful!

10:34.200 --> 10:35.550
I can't spend my whole life
playing the role of

10:34.210 --> 10:37.690
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

10:36.150 --> 10:39.000
a debauched wastrel,
drowning in luxury and carnal indulgence.

10:38.390 --> 10:41.190
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

10:40.000 --> 10:41.510
I must first be able to protect myself

10:41.510 --> 10:43.320
before I can protect the people
I want to protect.

10:42.030 --> 10:43.370
♪ And not be scared? ♪

10:43.400 --> 10:45.410
♪ A slight ripple ♪

10:44.030 --> 10:45.600
What does it really feel like

10:45.600 --> 10:49.190
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

10:45.790 --> 10:47.050
to truly love someone?

10:47.480 --> 10:48.720
To truly love someone

10:49.270 --> 10:50.790
is to feel what they feel.

10:49.470 --> 10:52.840
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

10:51.600 --> 10:53.200
You can sense his happiness,

10:53.810 --> 10:56.650
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

10:54.000 --> 10:55.200
so naturally, you can also feel

10:55.200 --> 10:57.130
the pain and struggle in his heart.

10:57.320 --> 11:00.690
♪ Let it be ♪

10:57.840 --> 10:59.630
You would find joy through him

11:01.360 --> 11:03.820
and naturally feel pain
through him as well.

11:11.630 --> 11:13.160
I, by the mandate of Heaven,

11:13.440 --> 11:15.040
reign over all under the sky!

11:15.240 --> 11:16.790
With clear rewards and punishments,

11:16.790 --> 11:18.750
I uphold the moral order of the realm.

11:18.750 --> 11:19.270
Now,

11:19.510 --> 11:22.240
it has been found that Li Lin,
Minister of Revenue,

11:22.240 --> 11:25.200
has embezzled the treasury and engaged in
malpractice for selfish ends.

11:25.200 --> 11:28.410
His crimes are beyond dispute,
a flagrant violation of heavenly law.

11:28.410 --> 11:30.050
By law, he is to be executed.

11:30.480 --> 11:32.720
I hereby order the execution
of his entire clan

11:32.720 --> 11:34.870
as a warning to all!

11:36.240 --> 11:37.390
It is noon.

11:37.960 --> 11:39.490
Prepare for the execution!

11:45.240 --> 11:45.910
Mother!

11:46.510 --> 11:47.670
Execute!

12:13.030 --> 12:13.630
Old man,

12:13.930 --> 12:15.990
how long are you going to keep me here?

12:17.990 --> 12:19.800
Not yet.

12:20.040 --> 12:23.200
Wait another hour until your son
comes back from the imperial court

12:23.200 --> 12:26.240
and tell us how things stand outside.

12:26.550 --> 12:27.790
Then I'll decide.

12:31.000 --> 12:32.920
He's just a sixth-rank deputy commander.

12:32.920 --> 12:34.600
Why did you let him go to the court?

12:34.600 --> 12:36.120
Not anymore.

12:36.870 --> 12:40.030
I had him resign on your behalf,
citing illness,

12:40.600 --> 12:42.390
and hand over your military tally

12:42.390 --> 12:44.390
as a show of loyalty to Li Yan.

12:45.240 --> 12:48.480
Li Yan has promoted him
three ranks as a reward.

12:48.920 --> 12:52.280
He is now a General.

12:54.750 --> 12:56.510
You asked him to hand over
my military command?

12:56.510 --> 12:57.940
Who gives you the right
to make decisions for me?

12:57.940 --> 12:58.580
Sun Di!

13:01.200 --> 13:02.930
You're my daughter's husband.

13:03.240 --> 13:05.600
What you do affects not only yourself

13:05.600 --> 13:06.790
but also the lives of

13:06.790 --> 13:08.450
my daughter and my whole clan!

13:10.660 --> 13:12.170
At a time like this,

13:12.960 --> 13:14.620
never mind military command—

13:15.320 --> 13:17.050
as long as we can keep our lives,

13:17.240 --> 13:18.840
even if you have to play the fool,

13:18.840 --> 13:20.310
you must keep playing along!

13:20.310 --> 13:22.960
Li Yan is nothing but a treasonous rebel
who usurped the throne!

13:22.960 --> 13:24.060
I'll lead my troops

13:24.480 --> 13:25.550
into the palace and kill him right now!

13:25.550 --> 13:26.350
And then what?

13:27.360 --> 13:28.760
The late emperor is dead.

13:29.000 --> 13:30.400
Who will take the throne?

13:30.720 --> 13:33.980
Who will take charge of
the overall situation in Biantang?

13:42.050 --> 13:43.110
Or do you...

13:44.840 --> 13:46.500
want to become the next Li Yan?

13:55.120 --> 13:56.200
Close the door

13:56.720 --> 13:58.050
and add a few more locks.

13:58.720 --> 14:00.510
No one is allowed in or out.

14:01.290 --> 14:04.200
Let this fool cool his head.

14:14.790 --> 14:17.310
The imperial edict of investiture
has been issued.

14:17.310 --> 14:18.790
You are now Empress.

14:19.240 --> 14:20.040
Your Majesty,

14:20.120 --> 14:22.000
why do you put yourself through this?

14:22.000 --> 14:23.200
Ask them all to leave.

14:24.240 --> 14:25.170
Your Majesty...

14:25.360 --> 14:27.840
His Majesty has arrived!

14:35.670 --> 14:36.320
Leave.

14:48.270 --> 14:48.840
Chun'er,

14:49.550 --> 14:50.350
what's wrong?

14:54.150 --> 14:56.350
I've been on the throne for over a month.

14:58.960 --> 15:00.240
Yet you still refuse to

15:01.370 --> 15:02.830
wear the empress's robes.

15:03.550 --> 15:05.550
And you've declined to accompany me

15:05.760 --> 15:07.820
to every state banquet and ceremony.

15:10.720 --> 15:12.720
What exactly are you unhappy about?

15:12.900 --> 15:15.700
You're now the most honored woman
in all the world.

15:15.770 --> 15:17.510
All the pain you've endured before

15:17.510 --> 15:18.790
is in the past.

15:19.150 --> 15:20.350
What more do you want?

15:20.840 --> 15:21.700
Or is it that...

15:23.120 --> 15:24.650
I have not treated you well?

15:25.550 --> 15:26.240
Li Yan.

15:28.750 --> 15:29.880
Who exactly are you?

15:35.730 --> 15:36.890
When I first met you,

15:38.270 --> 15:41.530
you said you were just a scion
of a noble family in Biantang.

15:41.870 --> 15:43.870
But when I came to Tangjing with you,

15:44.120 --> 15:46.180
I found out you were the Prince of Luo.

15:46.360 --> 15:47.630
I believed you,

15:48.600 --> 15:50.750
thinking you were marginalized
outside the imperial court

15:50.750 --> 15:51.960
and humiliated,

15:52.240 --> 15:53.360
so I wanted to help you
reclaim a little of

15:53.360 --> 15:55.820
the dignity
a royal descendant should have.

15:58.630 --> 16:00.120
But then you transformed

16:00.750 --> 16:02.240
into who you are now.

16:03.600 --> 16:05.840
It's not that I refuse to be your empress.

16:05.840 --> 16:07.080
I'm just bewildered—

16:07.870 --> 16:09.030
who are you, really?

16:09.480 --> 16:11.790
It feels as though I've never
truly known you.

16:11.790 --> 16:13.120
Will there come a day

16:13.720 --> 16:15.180
when I stand atop the walls

16:15.320 --> 16:17.920
of Tangjing
in my empress's ceremonial robes,

16:17.960 --> 16:18.840
only to die

16:19.960 --> 16:21.820
in your arms the very next moment?

16:24.870 --> 16:25.670
Zhao Chun'er,

16:25.790 --> 16:27.030
you think you are the only one

16:27.030 --> 16:29.160
who has suffered grievances and pain?

16:30.910 --> 16:32.270
If you don't want to

16:32.960 --> 16:34.490
wear the empress's attire,

16:35.600 --> 16:38.360
I won't force you.

16:43.240 --> 16:45.240
Biantang is in chaos right now.

16:45.510 --> 16:49.120
Just stay in the palace and rest well.

17:01.170 --> 17:02.280
[Ministry of War Office]

18:00.510 --> 18:01.440
Why are you here?

18:01.550 --> 18:02.750
How is General Xiuli?

18:03.200 --> 18:04.550
My situation is
a bit complicated right now.

18:04.550 --> 18:05.270
Lord Sun.

18:06.190 --> 18:06.800
You know

18:07.600 --> 18:08.730
what this is, right?

18:11.600 --> 18:12.640
Minister Xu!

18:13.240 --> 18:14.110
Minister Xu!

18:14.440 --> 18:15.160
Bad news!

18:15.830 --> 18:16.480
Sun Di...

18:16.640 --> 18:18.010
Sun Di has mobilized troops
from the Southeastern Guard Camp,

18:18.010 --> 18:20.070
50 li east of the city, into the palace!

18:20.070 --> 18:21.350
He may be plotting rebellion!

18:21.350 --> 18:22.070
Sun Di?

18:22.590 --> 18:23.720
The military tally is in my hands.

18:23.720 --> 18:24.830
How did he mobilize anyone?

18:24.830 --> 18:26.720
Go assemble
the imperial guards immediately.

18:26.720 --> 18:28.160
I'll go to the palace
to protect the Emperor myself.

18:28.160 --> 18:28.510
Yes, sir!

18:28.510 --> 18:29.240
Minister Xu!

18:29.590 --> 18:30.960
The Ministry of War has just sent word

18:30.960 --> 18:32.350
that someone broke into the office
last night,

18:32.350 --> 18:34.350
and the military tally
of the Southeastern Guards is missing!

18:34.350 --> 18:35.160
Come with me!

19:05.960 --> 19:07.070
You told me once

19:07.960 --> 19:09.360
that in this deep palace,

19:10.160 --> 19:12.000
power and the throne

19:12.640 --> 19:14.440
matter far more than blood ties.

19:14.750 --> 19:16.480
At first, I didn't understand.

19:17.590 --> 19:20.090
I even blamed you
for not wanting to acknowledge me.

19:20.090 --> 19:21.330
I'll take my leave.

19:21.680 --> 19:22.880
But now I understand.

19:23.400 --> 19:24.440
And I've done it—

19:24.970 --> 19:27.140
even better than you, Mother.

19:28.030 --> 19:30.290
And I understand it more deeply than you.

19:55.250 --> 19:55.900
Mother,

19:56.830 --> 19:58.090
if you were still alive

19:58.750 --> 20:00.280
and could see who I am today,

20:00.990 --> 20:02.320
you would probably be

20:03.310 --> 20:04.480
proud of me.

21:58.880 --> 21:59.960
I knew

22:00.400 --> 22:02.060
Xu Su's men couldn't kill you.

22:02.680 --> 22:04.480
I knew you would come back for me.

22:04.480 --> 22:06.400
You knew I'd come to kill you

22:06.830 --> 22:07.790
for Li Ce?

22:08.110 --> 22:09.000
I knew.

22:09.720 --> 22:10.830
But I'm not afraid.

22:11.240 --> 22:12.850
Because this is my fate.

22:13.590 --> 22:15.240
Li Ce was not your enemy.

22:15.680 --> 22:17.400
Why couldn't you let him go?

22:17.550 --> 22:18.950
From the very beginning,

22:19.590 --> 22:22.880
it was always one or the other—
Li Ce or me.

22:23.460 --> 22:24.720
If I hadn't killed him,

22:25.110 --> 22:27.770
one day he would've discovered
my true identity

22:27.880 --> 22:29.950
and moved to eliminate me all the same.

22:29.950 --> 22:31.320
He wouldn't.

22:42.830 --> 22:43.510
Move aside!

22:44.070 --> 22:46.360
I need to enter the palace
to see His Majesty!

22:46.360 --> 22:47.120
Lord Xu,

22:47.790 --> 22:50.430
I've received His Majesty's order
to protect him.

22:50.430 --> 22:52.490
No one is allowed to enter the palace.

22:53.830 --> 22:54.550
Go back.

22:54.680 --> 22:55.310
Sun Di,

22:55.960 --> 22:58.490
you're no longer
the Left General of Cavalry.

22:58.680 --> 23:01.350
Your son resigned on your behalf
two days ago,

23:01.350 --> 23:02.920
and His Majesty approved it!

23:02.920 --> 23:05.070
Otherwise, do you think
you and your family

23:05.070 --> 23:07.400
could still live peacefully in Biantang?

23:09.190 --> 23:10.720
The military tally is here.

23:12.240 --> 23:14.160
I'm acting on His Majesty's verbal decree.

23:14.160 --> 23:16.350
There are rebels among the imperial guards
in the capital.

23:16.350 --> 23:19.480
I was ordered to mobilize troops
from the Southeast Camp

23:19.680 --> 23:21.590
into the capital
to protect the Imperial City.

23:21.590 --> 23:24.370
By His Majesty's order, none may enter
without imperial authorization.

23:24.370 --> 23:25.500
How dare you, Sun Di!

23:25.550 --> 23:26.790
You broke into the Ministry of War Office

23:26.790 --> 23:28.480
and stole the military tally
of the Southeastern Guards!

23:28.480 --> 23:30.440
This is a capital crime that warrants
the execution of your entire clan!

23:30.440 --> 23:32.570
Lord Xu, you must be talking nonsense.

23:33.720 --> 23:36.790
His Majesty handed the military tally
to me personally.

23:36.790 --> 23:38.310
You must have forgotten.

23:39.700 --> 23:41.070
All soldiers, listen to my command!

23:41.070 --> 23:42.730
You're Biantang's soldiers!

23:42.790 --> 23:44.110
I'm the Minister of War!

23:44.110 --> 23:46.160
The criminal Sun Di
has stolen the military tally

23:46.160 --> 23:47.160
and committed treason!

23:47.160 --> 23:48.640
Seize him immediately!

23:51.590 --> 23:52.830
The military tally is here!

23:52.830 --> 23:54.360
I am the General of Cavalry!

23:54.720 --> 23:55.930
Who dares move?

23:58.310 --> 23:59.160
Li Ce

23:59.550 --> 24:02.880
was never worthy of this dragon robe
from the day he was born!

24:18.590 --> 24:19.480
General Chu,

24:20.640 --> 24:23.030
this is a family matter
between Li Ce and me.

24:23.030 --> 24:24.830
You didn't have to get involved.

24:25.070 --> 24:26.590
Li Ce helped you,

24:27.320 --> 24:29.000
but he also did it to use you.

24:29.230 --> 24:30.630
If you hadn't helped him,

24:30.830 --> 24:33.440
he wouldn't have sat on that throne
for even a single day.

24:33.440 --> 24:34.770
If you hadn't saved him,

24:35.270 --> 24:37.870
he might have been killed
by my mother long ago.

24:39.640 --> 24:40.110
Yes.

24:41.240 --> 24:42.830
She was also his mother.

24:43.880 --> 24:44.960
Come to think of it,

24:45.750 --> 24:48.510
we were true brothers by blood.

24:57.400 --> 24:58.750
Did you not help Li Ce

24:59.160 --> 25:01.440
simply to rebuild your Xiuli Army?

25:01.990 --> 25:04.120
You and Li Ce were allies, true enough,

25:04.590 --> 25:06.590
but I can give you all of that too.

25:43.750 --> 25:44.880
In the royal family,

25:45.830 --> 25:47.830
even blood ties mean nothing—

25:48.480 --> 25:51.440
let alone the meager friendship
between you two.

25:51.750 --> 25:52.680
How can

25:53.480 --> 25:56.010
friendship be more reliable
than interests?

25:56.240 --> 25:57.200
What do you want?

25:57.640 --> 25:58.710
General Xiuli?

25:59.110 --> 26:00.070
Prince of Xiuli?

26:01.000 --> 26:02.510
Or Queen Xiuli?

26:02.750 --> 26:04.350
An assassin is in the palace!

26:04.640 --> 26:06.170
Soldiers, heed my command—

26:06.400 --> 26:08.660
enter the palace to protect His Majesty!

26:22.070 --> 26:23.160
General Chu,

26:24.480 --> 26:26.880
we can make a deal.

27:05.270 --> 27:05.880
Li Yan,

27:06.740 --> 27:07.740
Li Ce was not

27:07.760 --> 27:09.830
a bargaining chip for power.

27:11.200 --> 27:12.790
He was my friend.

28:18.350 --> 28:19.960
The new Emperor Li Yan is dead.

28:19.960 --> 28:21.160
There is no need to protect him.

28:21.160 --> 28:22.920
Chu Qiao has assassinated the Emperor!

28:22.920 --> 28:24.350
Her crime is unforgivable!

28:24.350 --> 28:26.550
Kill Chu Qiao immediately!

28:52.960 --> 28:54.820
Xu Su, guilty of treason and regicide,

28:54.820 --> 28:56.350
has already been executed!

28:56.510 --> 28:57.750
Soldiers, hear my command!

28:57.750 --> 29:00.750
Seize all of his personal guards!

29:01.820 --> 29:04.020
Imperial guards who acted unknowingly

29:04.510 --> 29:06.110
under Xu Su's orders—

29:07.070 --> 29:07.830
surrender,

29:09.160 --> 29:10.560
and you will be pardoned!

29:22.830 --> 29:26.450
♪ The dust in the world ♪

29:26.970 --> 29:30.440
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

29:28.880 --> 29:31.680
Qiao is the world-renowned General Chu.

29:31.150 --> 29:33.950
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

29:32.150 --> 29:34.830
"General Chu Meets
the Crown Prince of Biantang By Chance—

29:34.780 --> 29:36.130
♪ And not be scared? ♪

29:35.160 --> 29:38.310
Fake Drama Turns Into Real Fate."

29:36.150 --> 29:38.170
♪ A slight ripple ♪

29:38.350 --> 29:41.940
♪ Floating life hangs by a thread ♪

29:42.220 --> 29:45.590
♪ The more pulled, the softer it gets ♪

29:43.920 --> 29:44.960
Qiao...

29:46.560 --> 29:49.410
♪ Who dares to say forever? ♪

29:50.070 --> 29:53.440
♪ Let it be ♪

29:54.520 --> 29:57.950
♪ Grudges and grace
were never meant to be ♪

29:56.640 --> 29:57.270
Qiao,

29:57.920 --> 30:00.030
I'm giving
these 3,000 imperial guards to you.

29:58.430 --> 30:01.440
♪ Why must you take and demand so much? ♪

30:00.790 --> 30:02.510
They shall guard you just as they

30:01.820 --> 30:03.450
♪ Go weaving ♪

30:03.160 --> 30:03.880
protect me.

30:03.780 --> 30:08.730
♪ Grand and glorious excuses ♪

30:04.680 --> 30:05.310
Li Ce,

30:05.880 --> 30:08.240
I haven't fulfilled my promise to you yet.

30:09.250 --> 30:12.050
♪ We once beheld ♪

30:12.070 --> 30:15.480
♪ A mirage on earth ♪

30:17.200 --> 30:19.840
♪ Beauty never ♪

30:19.860 --> 30:24.590
♪ Lasts for long ♪

30:22.600 --> 30:23.760
[Mihe Abode]

30:24.860 --> 30:28.380
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

30:28.410 --> 30:32.840
♪ It's just a stone ♪

30:33.140 --> 30:40.350
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

30:39.160 --> 30:39.750
Xing.

30:42.270 --> 30:43.750
I want to avenge Li Ce.

30:44.000 --> 30:45.600
I must kill the Prince of Luo!

30:45.960 --> 30:46.640
Xing,

30:47.110 --> 30:48.370
Li Yan is already dead.

30:48.700 --> 30:50.630
You killed him with your own hands.

30:51.480 --> 30:52.310
No!

31:01.750 --> 31:02.310
Xing.

31:04.920 --> 31:06.680
Everything is over now.

31:07.880 --> 31:09.550
Li Ce has been avenged.

31:11.110 --> 31:12.240
It's all in the past.

31:17.720 --> 31:18.830
It's all over now?

31:28.070 --> 31:29.110
You've done

31:30.110 --> 31:31.370
everything you could.

31:32.200 --> 31:33.440
And you did it well.

31:38.750 --> 31:40.960
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

31:41.080 --> 31:43.620
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

31:42.200 --> 31:42.830
You can

31:44.060 --> 31:45.360
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

31:44.400 --> 31:45.510
leave it all behind now.

31:45.380 --> 31:46.840
♪ My longing surges ♪

31:46.870 --> 31:49.380
♪ I become haggard ♪

31:49.990 --> 31:52.430
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

31:52.470 --> 31:55.290
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

31:55.310 --> 31:57.010
♪ My love remains ♪

31:57.320 --> 32:00.690
♪ But you're already gone ♪

32:00.720 --> 32:02.990
♪ What I seek in life ♪

32:03.010 --> 32:04.600
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

32:04.620 --> 32:07.210
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

32:07.230 --> 32:08.820
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

32:08.840 --> 32:12.030
♪ My longing still rests ♪

32:12.050 --> 32:14.410
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

32:14.440 --> 32:15.950
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

32:15.980 --> 32:18.630
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

32:18.650 --> 32:23.510
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

32:23.540 --> 32:24.940
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

32:24.960 --> 32:27.210
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

32:27.230 --> 32:29.680
♪ How do we start over? ♪

32:29.700 --> 32:33.010
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

32:33.040 --> 32:35.290
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

32:35.320 --> 32:38.730
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

32:38.750 --> 32:41.070
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

32:41.090 --> 32:43.970
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

32:44.000 --> 32:48.540
♪ In the end ♪

32:50.170 --> 32:54.380
♪ It can only be praised ♪

33:16.880 --> 33:18.400
A weak ruler over a strong state

33:18.400 --> 33:20.880
is an omen of instability for the nation!

33:21.070 --> 33:23.440
General Xiuli, Chu Qiao,
is hereby conferred

33:23.440 --> 33:24.700
the title of Imperial Consort Xiuli!

33:24.700 --> 33:26.190
I'll leave the 500 guards

33:26.850 --> 33:28.160
Li Ce promised me to you.

33:28.160 --> 33:29.920
Where have you gone now?

33:30.110 --> 33:30.720
Miss!

33:31.160 --> 33:32.430
I have a favor to ask of you.

33:32.430 --> 33:34.200
No matter how the royal clan schemes

33:34.200 --> 33:35.720
or how chaotic the world becomes,

33:35.720 --> 33:37.690
nothing shall ever separate us again.

33:37.690 --> 33:38.350
Don't come over.

33:38.350 --> 33:39.030
Don't come over!
